title: 'The Circle’ Season 4, Episodes 1-4 | Netflix and Spill
description:
The Ringer’s Jomi Adeniran and Jodi Walker recap the first four episodes of Season 4 of Netflix’s ‘The Circle.’ They go through all the new players and catfishes, who has the best and worst games, and the biggest twist in 'Circle' history.
Hosts: Jomi Adeniran and Jodi Walker
Producers: Sasha Ashall and Chelsea Stark-Jones
